ch.obermuhlner.jhuge.collection.builder

Interface MapBuilder<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the key in the Map
    V - the type of the value in the Map
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHugeMapBuilder, HugeHashMap.Builder, ImmutableHugeHashMap.Builder

    public interface MapBuilder<K,V>
    Builds a Map.

    The concrete implementations of this API are typically inner classes of the collection class they are building.
